### scan SSID's:
#
# nice compact interface CLI, also wpa_cli seems to be most modern package, part of wpa_supplicant :
# active/new scan:
sudo wpa_cli scan
# show last scan:
sudo wpa_cli scan_results
#
##
# active/new scan:
sudo iwlist wlan0 scan 
# show last scan:
sudo iwlist wlan0 scan last

